# GitHub Linguist language statistics for the Tauri rewrite.
#
# The active rewrite lives in web-ui/src and web-ui/src-tauri. The original WPF
# tree is kept as a compatibility/reference source for the display host and
# should not dominate the repository language bar.
###############################################################################

# Legacy/reference implementations
FluentFlyoutWPF/** linguist-vendored
fluent_flyout_rs/** linguist-vendored
docs/** linguist-documentation

# Generated dependency locks and Tauri schemas
**/Cargo.lock linguist-generated
**/package-lock.json linguist-generated
web-ui/src-tauri/gen/** linguist-generated

# Static prototype files kept for reference after the Svelte/Tauri migration
web-ui/app.js linguist-vendored
web-ui/styles.css linguist-vendored

# Binary/image assets
*.png binary linguist-generated
*.ico binary linguist-generated
*.zip binary linguist-generated
*.exe binary linguist-generated
*.dll binary linguist-generated
*.msi binary linguist-generated

